e onscreen images larger.</p><p>To change these preferences, choose Apple menu <img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/5BFDD3F8094622802EEE504F/5BFDD3F9094622802EEE5056/en_US/e043ddf1a45711e13f0b30612db65e21.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"30\" width=\"26\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/IL_AppleLogo.png\"> &gt; System Preferences, then click Mouse.</p><p><a href=\"x-help-action://openPrefPane?bundleId=com.apple.preference.mouse\" class=\"URL\">Open Mouse preferences for me</a></p><div class=\"Alert\"><p class=\"Note\"><em>Note: </em>A wireless mouse must be connected with your Mac—or a four-button mouse must be plugged into your Mac—to display the preferences listed below.</p></div><div id=\"mchl82d42460\" class=\"Subhead\"><h2 class=\"Name\">Wireless mouse</h2><table data-type=\"Multicolumn\" aria-label=\"Point and click wireless mouse System Preferences\"><thead><tr><th colspan=\"4\" scope=\"col\"><p class=\"TableHead\">Point &amp; Click</p></th><th colspan=\"8\" scope=\"col\"></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p>Scroll direction: Natural</p></td><td colspan=\"8\"><p>Select this option to move the contents of a window in the same direction as your fingers.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p>Secondary click</p></td><td colspan=\"8\"><p>Select the option, then choose “Click on the right side,” or “Click on the left side” to secondary click (or Control-click) items on the screen.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p>Smart zoom</p></td><td colspan=\"8\"><p>Select this option to double-tap with one finger to zoom in or out.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p>Tracking speed</p></td><td colspan=\"8\"><p>Adjust the speed at which the pointer follows the movement of your mouse.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table data-type=\"Multicolumn\" aria-label=\"More gestures wireless mouse System Preferences\"><thead><tr><th colspan=\"4\" scope=\"col\"><p class=\"TableHead\">More Gestures</p></th><th colspan=\"8\" scope=\"col\"></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p>Swipe between pages</p></td><td colspan=\"8\"><p>Select this option, then choose the gesture to use to move between pages in a document.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p>Swipe between full-screen apps</p></td><td colspan=\"8\"><p>Select this option to move between apps in full screen.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p>Mission Control</p></td><td colspan=\"8\"><p>Select this option to double-tap with two fingers to enter Mission Control.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"mchl5b14aba3\" class=\"Subhead\"><h2 class=\"Name\">Apple four-button mouse</h2><table data-type=\"Multicolumn\" aria-label=\"Apple four-button mouse System Preferences\"><thead><tr><th colspan=\"4\" scope=\"col\"><p class=\"TableHead\">Options</p></th><th colspan=\"8\" scope=\"col\"></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p>Scroll direction: Natural</p></td><td colspan=\"8\"><p>Select this option to move the contents of a window in the same direction as your fingers.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p>Tracking speed</p></td><td colspan=\"8\"><p>Adjust the speed at which the pointer follows the movement of your mouse.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p>Scrolling</p></td><td colspan=\"8\"><p>Adjust how quickly the pointer moves when you scroll.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p>Double-Click</p></td><td colspan=\"8\"><p>Adjust how rapidly you must click for your Mac to recognize a double-click.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p>Primary Button</p></td><td colspan=\"8\"><p>Select this option, then choose this gesture to secondary click (or Control-click) items on the screen.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p>Secondary Button</p></td><td colspan=\"8\"><p>Displays shortcut (contextual) menus—the same as Control-clicking a one-button mouse.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p>Mission Control, Show App Windows, Show Desktop, Dashboard, App Switcher, and Spotlight</p></td><td colspan=\"8\"><p>Press both side buttons at once to activate one of these features.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p>Other</p></td><td colspan=\"8\"><p>Opens an app of your choosing.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p>Off</p></td><td colspan=\"8\"><p>Deactivates the button.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p>Scrolling</p></td><td colspan=\"8\"><p>Choose an option to adjust how the pointer behaves in windows and lists when you scroll. (The scroll ball doesn’t scroll menus or sliders in dialogs.)</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"LinkUniversal\"><strong>See also</strong><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=connect-an-apple-wireless-accessory&amp;version=10.14&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MCHLP2656&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=10.14\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">Connect an Apple wireless accessory with Mac</a></div></body>","tags":[{"type":"audience","refKey":"PUBLIC_USERS","tagPath":"audience/PUBLIC_USERS","title":"Public"}]}]},"categoryInfo":{"categories":["DisplayVersion/macOS Mojave 10.14","IP-Meta/DesignVersion/DesignVersion2","platform/mac","ContentMode/liveContent","ArchivalStatus/Unarchived","MetaFollow/MetaFollowOFF","ExternalIndex/ExternalIndexON","SupportSearchIndex/SupportSearchIndexON"],"categoryDictionaries":[{"key":"SupportSearchIndexON","name":"SupportSearchIndexON","englishName":"SupportSearchIndexON","displayName":"SupportSearchIndexON","articleCount":"3950"},{"key":"liveContent","name":"Live Content","englishName":"Live Content","displayName":"Live Content","articleCount":"7864"},{"key":"IP-Meta","name":"IP-Meta","englishName":"IP-Meta","displayName":"IP-Meta","articleCount":"0"},{"key":"Unarchived","name":"Unarchived","englishName":"Unarchived","displayName":"Unarchived","articleCount":"10186"},{"key":"ContentMode","name":"ContentMode","englishName":"ContentMode","displayName":"ContentMode","articleCount":"0"},{"key":"ExternalIndexON","name":"ExternalIndexON","englishName":"ExternalIndexON","displayName":"ExternalIndexON","articleCount":"